{
  "stem": "22586.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The way we have found out about these things, that occasionally apparently when these people were shot down, there were children who survived by having other people fall on top of them so they-- they were not killed and that somehow they found their way backs.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And-- and they were the ones who told other people.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So they said, no, these children are imagining things.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It cannot be happening.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So as I say, we did hear.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But we didn't want to believe that anything like that is going on.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Couldn't imagine that it could be true.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Did everybody follow voluntarily when these placards were put up to go to the different places assigned?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Did anybody try to escape?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was really no way to escape, because [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] the Hungarian people-- if-- if somebody did, the Hungarian people would report them to the German authorities.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was no place to go to, because certainly Hungarian neighbors were not willing to help us, to hide anybody.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So there was just no way of doing it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Germans confiscated it from Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In fact, my very good friend who I mentioned lives in West Orange now, Edith Alice, her grandfather owned the lumberyard.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Excuse me.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I have to blow my nose.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "On May 16th, we were told again that we have to get all our belongings, and we have to go to the railroad station.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were all herded up.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were taken to the railroad station.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We didn't know where we were going.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they put us into [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the cattle cars, railroad cars without windows.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And hundreds of people in one train-- in one car actually.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
